This is the README file for Language::Haskell, a module that provides
Perl bindings to Haskell's, via an embedded "Hugs" environment.

Please type "perldoc Language::Haskell" after installation to
see the module usage information.

* Installation

Language::Haskell uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

